headline: How Fifth Third Bancorp, Merck, And Duke Energy Can Put Cash In Your Pocket
summary: Companies with a long history of paying dividends and consistently hiking them remain appealing to income-focused investors. Fifth Third Bancorp, Merck, and Duke Energy have rewarded shareholders for years and recently announced dividend increases. ...
